00:12:01,805 --> 00:12:04,225
They represent the flora and fauna of the crucible.

262
00:12:04,966 --> 00:12:07,926
The beasts, fairies, and witches that live in the wilds,

263
00:12:08,766 --> 00:12:11,267
either by choice or because they've been shunned

